text.tspan: In this task, you will see a sequence of
letters. Each letter is shown for a few
seconds. You need to decide if you saw
the same letter 3 trials ago, that is, this
If you saw the same letter 3 trials ago,
you type the letter M (M for Memory). If
it was Not a letter shown 3 trials ago, you
press the space bar to next info screen
For example, if you get the letters, and
A B L T B R H I R
n n n n m n n n m
This is actually very difficult! So you need
some time to get better at it. When you
respond correct, you see the bars around
the key turn green, and red if wrong!
press the letter "q" to start, or up arrow
